fields.name: Skort jumpsuit
fields.description: Calling this piece a shorts jumpsuit doesn't really do it justice. Languid, slinky, and that elusive combo of glam and comfort.

fields.name: Batik sundress
fields.description: Go from day to night in this bright, flattering dress.

fields.name: Polarized sunglasses
fields.description: See everything with the utmost crispness in any natural lighting.

fields.name: Sunglasses, with built-in earrings!
fields.description: Accused of over-accessorizing? Prove them wrong, there's no such thing.

fields.name: Carhartt x Nike
fields.description: I guess Carhartt makes shoes now? Or Nike makes Carhartts? Who can keep up, but I have to say I love these.

fields.name: T-shirt
fields.description: This skeleton is ready to peace right out.

fields.name: Tomato crewneck
fields.description: Get ready for heirloom season with this comfy sweater!

fields.name: Key necklace
fields.description: Inspired by when we were kids and carried our housekey like this. But with Swarovski crystals!

fields.name: Black leather Nikes
fields.description: You can wear these with dressier clothes than most sneakers would dare. But not with motorcycle leathers.

fields.name: Epic hammer
fields.description: When you have this hammer, all your problems will start to look like a Loki.

fields.name: Fresh cut fruit
fields.description: Ready to mix up and sit poolside.

fields.name: Replica Apple Watch
fields.description: Use your phone to keep track of your workouts, but want a timepiece that's au courant? This is your answer.  We don't need any stinkin' numbers, we're adults here!

fields.name: Tall stool or small table
fields.description: Need extra seating on hand, or a base for a large planter? We've got you covered.

fields.name: Minimalist bedframe
fields.description: Sleek, squarish, but oh-so-dreamy. Set up your room like a chic hotel!

fields.name: Salt bae poster
fields.description: Probably just out of frame, salt bae is dusting this fresh food with the exact perfect seasoning.

fields.name: Mouthwatering focaccia poster
fields.description: Is this focaccia or pastry dough? Are those banana slices? With this on your wall, your guests who couldn't decide if the dress was blue or gold will have a heyday.

fields.name: Cool coffee table book
fields.description: It doesn't have to live on a coffee table, looks pretty good on this stool actually.

fields.name: Indoor/ Outdoor bench
fields.description: Grace your entryway, front yard or back porch with this simple yet sturdy bench.
